        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/735/629/original/56c82edb-302c-4466-aee8-e600f7950d2a.png" srcset="" alt="Open Student Submission" height="327" width="367">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_b6037842-feea-4000-bd16-f916ec981072" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Use the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-student-list-to-view-student-submissions-in/ta-p/770" target="_blank">student list</a> to locate a student submission.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-rubric" data-step-uuid="426237d7-db11-4247-955d-e75ebd41c703">
    <h2 id="view-rubric" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Rubric</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/735/633/original/de9cfebb-f8d5-4d65-a2c5-d33b8087f3df.png" srcset="" alt="View Rubric" height="188" width="163">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_d0d61f45-f558-4c57-ad77-823cb46a1b31" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>View Rubric</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="resize-rubric" data-step-uuid="6a38f509-2a32-4d83-900c-67b5370424e1">
    <h3 id="resize-rubric" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Resize Rubric</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/098/685/original/adbada38-0a98-4202-a1f3-da35fb58f86c.png" srcset="" alt="Resize Rubric" height="451" width="781">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1ff8a019-6571-4fb2-a3f2-a6f61a13d749" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view the entire rubric window, you may need to scroll both vertically and horizontally. To resize the rubric window, click and drag the sizing column horizontally.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="complete-rubric" data-step-uuid="6063d594-13a2-490c-9409-db3b3ffa4b4e">
    <h2 id="complete-rubric" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Complete Rubric</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/433/660/original/5a1ea6a7-f51d-483c-bd38-14b3281f0584.png" srcset="" alt="Complete Rubric" height="408" width="748">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_cd3ffc08-2559-44d1-b1c0-4b024aa57208" class="text-block-content">
    <p>For each criterion, click the rating that applies to the student's submission [1].</p>
<p>You can also add a comment for each rubric criterion by clicking the <strong>Comment</strong> icon [2].</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> To deselect a rating, click the rating assigned [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

